    • Animal

      public Animal​(java.lang.String imageLink, waterArea waterDeathArea, double SpawnPositionX, double SpawnPositionY, coordinateArea Border)
      Parameters:
      imageLink - set the start image of the Animal
      waterDeathArea - waterArea class which will check if your in water
      SpawnPositionX - spawn X position of the Animal
      SpawnPositionY - spawn Y position of the Animal
      Border - takes in coordinateArea class, the border of the map that the Animal cannot go pass
